&lt;h3 id="ai-enhanced-workflow-diagram"&gt;AI-Enhanced Workflow Diagram&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To visualize how AI tools can enhance team collaboration, here&amp;rsquo;s a simple workflow diagram.&lt;/p&gt;
